'''槍蝦科'''（學名：{{lang|la|Alpheidae}}）{{r|TaiBNET}}，又名'''鼓虾科'''<ref name="blueanimalbio">{{cite book |chapter-url=http://www.blueanimalbio.com/bugs/ruanjia/zhenxia.htm |chapter=真虾下目 Caridea |url=http://www.blueanimalbio.com/ |title=蓝色动物学 |language=zh-hans |access-date=2013-01-12 |date=2012-07-31 |archive-date=2011-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110128174951/http://www.blueanimalbio.com/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，是[[真蝦下目|真蝦下目]][[槍蝦總科|槍蝦總科]]的其中一個科，特徵是兩邊的爪不對稱，而較大那邊的爪可發出巨響，就如槍聲一樣，因而得名（详见[[鼓虾|鼓虾]]）。

槍蝦科在世界的分布廣泛而且分散，包括有約600個品種，可分成最少38個屬<ref name="multiple">{{cite journal |authors=A. Anker, S. T. Ahyong, P. Y. Noel, and A. R. Palmer |title=Morphological phylogeny of alpheid shrimps: parallel preadaptation and the origin of a key morphological innovation, the snapping claw |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_evolution_2006-12_60_12/page/2507 |journal=[[Evolution|Evolution]] |volume=60 |issue=12 |year=2006 |pages=2507–2528 |doi=10.1554/05-486.1 | pmid = 17263113 |language=en }}</ref>。當中最重要的兩個屬是[[槍蝦屬|槍蝦屬]]（{{lang|la|''Alpheus''}}）和[[合鼓蝦屬|合鼓蝦屬]]（{{lang|la|''Synalpheus''}}），分別有超過250種和100種<ref>{{cite journal |first1=W. |last1=Kim |first2=L. G. |last2=Abele |title=The snapping shrimp genus ''Alpheus'' from the Eastern Pacific (Decapoda: Caridea: Alpheidae) |journal={{tsl|en|Smithsonian Contributions to Zoology|Smithsonian Contributions to Zoology}} |volume=454 |year=1988 |pages=1–119 |url=http://si-pddr.si.edu/dspace/bitstream/10088/5122/2/SCtZ-0454-Lo_res.pdf |language=en |access-date=2013-01-13 |archive-date=2012-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312041649/http://si-pddr.si.edu/dspace/bitstream/10088/5122/2/SCtZ-0454-Lo_res.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author={{tsl|en|Fenner A. Chace, Jr.|Fenner A. Chace, Jr.}} |title=The Caridean Shrimps (Crustacea: Decapoda) of the Albatross Philippine Expedition, 1907–1910, Part 5: Family Alpheidae |journal={{tsl|en|Smithsonian Contributions to Zoology|Smithsonian Contributions to Zoology}} |volume=466 |year=1988 |pages=1–99 |url=http://si-pddr.si.edu/dspace/bitstream/10088/5144/3/SCtZ-0466-Hi_res.pdf |access-date=2013-01-13 |archive-date=2012-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312041821/http://si-pddr.si.edu/dspace/bitstream/10088/5144/3/SCtZ-0466-Hi_res.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。槍蝦科的物種會在[[珊瑚礁|珊瑚礁]]、[[海床|海床]]上的[[海草|海草]]和[[牡蠣礁|牡蠣礁]]居住，還會在居所挖洞穴來捕獵。幾乎所有本科的物種均在熱帶和溫帶的沿海和海洋水域中發現，就只有棲息於寒冷海洋的[[乙鼓蝦屬|乙鼓蝦屬]]（{{lang|la|''Betaeus''}}）跟只在淡水洞穴發現的[[溪槍蝦屬|溪槍蝦屬]]（{{lang|la|''Potamalpheops''}}）。

在蝦群裡，槍蝦科物種的水下通信和聲納會互相干擾<ref name="BBC2">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/935855.stm |title=Shrimp, bubble and pop |date=2000-09-21 |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |accessdate=2011-07-02 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108122034/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/935855.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2000/09/26/science/sleuths-solve-case-of-bubble-mistaken-for-a-snapping-shrimp.html |title=Sleuths solve case of bubble mistaken for a snapping shrimp |author=Kenneth Chang |date=2000-09-26 |publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |page=5 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117121820/https://www.nytimes.com/2000/09/26/science/sleuths-solve-case-of-bubble-mistaken-for-a-snapping-shrimp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F20E16F9355A107A93C0A91789D85F438485F9 |title=Sea creatures trouble sonar operators – new enzyme |publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=2011-07-02 |date=1947-02-02 |language=en |archive-date=2014-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140218220637/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F20E16F9355A107A93C0A91789D85F438485F9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這些蝦群發出的聲音，是海洋中噪聲的主要來源<ref name="BBC2"/>。

